name: Symphonic Warrior Haarp
text:
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned by tributing 2 "Symphonic Warrior" monsters you control. This card gains effects based on the number of face-up "Symph" cards you control with different names.
1+ All "Symphonic Warrior" monsters you control gain 500 ATK
2+ This card is unaffected by your opponent’s monster effects.
3+ (Quick Effect): Once per turn, you can target 1 face-up card on the field; negate its effects.
4+ "Symph" cards you control cannot be targeted or destroyed by your opponent’s card effects.
If this card you control leaves the field because of an opponent’s card: Special Summon up to 2 "Symphonic Warrior" monsters from your GY except "Symphonic Warrior Haarp".
